<subSubSection id="C3266549FF95FFE91343FDCB71B2FDD5" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="8B8336C2FF95FFE91343FDCB71B2FDD5" blockId="22.[264,1323,284,590]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">
<emphasis id="B948EAD0FF95FFE91343FDCB71A8FDBE" bold="true" box="[312,465,523,549]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Distribution</emphasis>
. Widely distributed in Asia. A neustonic form inhabiting microsites near fresh cold water.
</paragraph>
